profile_summary:
I'm Eduardo Pino, a seasoned developer with expertise in JavaScript and CSS. I've been actively contributing to the community through my 29 public repositories, showcasing my skills in building scalable and maintainable web applications. With a passion for writing clean, modular code, I aim to deliver robust solutions that meet real-world problems. 

A strong advocate for JavaScript and CSS, I continue to push the boundaries of what's possible with these technologies, leveraging their versatility to drive innovation in the ever-evolving tech landscape. As a collaborative developer, I look forward to connecting with like-minded professionals who share my enthusiasm for software development.
